    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to be parting with this beauty, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve truly babied it since day one! It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom. If you're looking for a ride that's been meticulously cared for and is ready for the road, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
