    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 inline-six with an impeccably maintained VANOS system and individual throttle bodies. This chassis has undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a complete suspension refresh using OEM bushings to preserve factory-spec lateral kinematics and turn-in response. The Getrag six-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Compression and leak-down numbers are consistent across all cylinders, reflecting a life of meticulous, climate-controlled ownership. The exterior retains its original factory luster with no signs of oxidation or clear coat failure, while the interior cabin remains a time capsule with zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrumentation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
