    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a true time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster from every angle. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather is still supple and carries that distinct new-car aroma, with absolutely zero wear on the bolsters, steering wheel, or carpets. Every switch, button, and digital interface operates with crisp, tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine OEM parts. This is a collector-grade specimen that performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The sale includes a comprehensive service dossier, all original manuals, and both sets of factory keys. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 45500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
