    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in showroom-equivalent condition, boasting flawless aesthetics and peak mechanical performance. A definitive acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this unit has been meticulously preserved to ensure it remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
