    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly incredible, like-new condition\u2014seriously, it still has that fresh car smell! I've babied this thing from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and getting it detailed regularly. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself just how pristine it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
